<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.13">
<l>tampara mallaṉa vāṇmaika ḷaittaṉi yēniṉṟu tāmcey vārō</l>
<l>vemperu māṉuṉṉaip peṟṟa vayiṟuṭai yēṉiṉi yāṉeṉ ceykēṉ</l>
<l>ampara mēḻu matiru miṭikura laṅkaṉaṟ ceṅka ṇuṭai</l>
<l>vampaviḻ kāṉattu mālviṭai yōṭu piṇaṅkinī vantāy pōlum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Should [someone], standing alone, perform heroics,</l>
<l rend="indent">things that are not of his ability?</l>
<l>My lord, I whose stomach begot you what shall I do now?</l>
<l>It seems you came to a forest where fragrance wafts</l>
<l rend="indent">and there tangled with a black bull</l>
<l>With burning red eyes and a thunderous bellow that shook the seven heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
